Sentencas: Powders of the perovskite of nominal composition Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-delta (SCFC) were prepared by a modified citrate route in order to determine its structural and micro structural characteristics.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of the Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-δ perovskite as cathode material for ITSOFCs

Sentencas: In this study, the interpretation of the X-ray diffraction has been performed based on a diagonal perovskite.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of the Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-δ perovskite as cathode material for ITSOFCs

Sentencas: However, electron diffraction demonstrates that the microstructure is rather more complex than that deduced from the average cell root2a(p) x 2a(p) x root2a(p).
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of the Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-δ perovskite as cathode material for ITSOFCs

Sentencas: Two reflections in the selected area electron diffraction may be interpreted as first-order satellites, of different basic reflections, arising from an incommensurate modulation along the b* direction (b approximate to 2.4a(p) Angstrom).
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of the Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-δ perovskite as cathode material for ITSOFCs

Sentencas: Symmetrical electrodes of Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-delta powders were deposited on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (CGO) ceramic pellets, and the electrochemical properties of the interfaces between the porous cathodes (SCFC) and the electrolyte (CGO) have been investigated at intermediate temperatures (500-766 degreesC) using AC impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of the Sr0.8Ce0.1Fe0.7Co0.3O3-δ perovskite as cathode material for ITSOFCs

Sentencas: SCFC electrodes exhibited an area-specific resistivity (ASR) at 700 degreesC of 0.86 Omega cm(2).
